data.description: Sprawling Ranch Home in desirable Monfort heights! One Story Living in this wonderful family home located within Green Township! 4th bedroom in partially finished Lower Level, and an incredible overall space for flexibility! Roof, Mechanicals, Windows approximately 10 years old. WBFP, Deck. Primed for your selective updates, a nice solid value, ready for your vision! Large Level Lot, 1st floor Laundry, No Outlet Street. convenient to everything via North bend Road and I-74/I-275.
